## Quick Start

```python
from machine import {{ machine_class_name(model) }}

machine = {{ machine_class_name(model) }}()
machine.cycle()
print(machine.current_state_path)
print(machine.vars)
```

To send events, pass event paths or compatible relative event names to
`cycle(...)`:

```python
machine.cycle(['{{ model.root_state.name }}'])
```

